name: Jabba's Haven
Lore: 'Jabba has won the service of many of his guards and other henchbeings through games of chance.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. May deploy Nal Hutta. Once per game, may retrieve an alien or [Independent] starship into hand. While Fearless And Inventive on table, once per battle, may lose 1 force; your battle destiny modifiers affect your total battle destiny instead. (Immune to Alter.)',
